import React from 'react' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' export default function Alluserdetail({userdetail,setuserdetail,handleInput}) { const Alldata=useSelector((state)=>state.userdata) const data=Alldata.ata console.log(data) return (<>

Confirm Details

First Name: {data.fname} Last Name: {data.lname} Email: {data.email} Gender: {data.sex} Phone: {data.phone} First Book: {data.fbook} Second Book: {data.sbook} Third Book: {data.tbook} Author: {data.author}
) }
